text: Brooke Levi Vincent (born 4 June 1992) is an English actress. She is known for her role as Sophie Webster in the ITV soap opera Coronation Street, which she played from 2004 to 2019. Vincent was born in Audenshaw, Greater Manchester, England. == Other websites == * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:English child actors Category:English television actors Category:Actors from Greater Manchester
